  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/e8e845fca660c07d7ce0e3bdaa35538c.gif?t=1765235894\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/e8e845fca660c07d7ce0e3bdaa35538c.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Heroes with unique weapons, abilities, and talents<br></li><li>Over 70 weapons<br></li><li>Weapon fusion system<br></li><li>Over 200 passive abilities for building your build<br></li><li>Racial Abilities<br></li><li>Pets<br></li><li>Runes<br></li><li>Bestiary<br></li><li>Over 20 hours of content<br></li><li>Bosses with unique abilities<br></li><li>Thousands of unlockables<br></li><li>Long character progression<br></li><li>Runs perfectly on Steam Deck<br></li><li>Supports Ultrawide<br></li><li>Day and Night Cycle<br></li><li>Endless Mode</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Starting</strong></h2>Hunt during the day, be hunted during the NIGHT! Fight bizarre monsters that will terrify you at night! Strengthen your hero by collecting relics, familiars from around the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Day & Night Cycle</strong></h2>Look for relics and vendors that only spawn at night.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weather Events</strong></h2>Be prepared!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a8d73bdba79e6492c50e0664.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a8d73bdba79e6492c50e0664.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a8d73bdba79e6492c50e0664.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/bb872e5b506c4fcbb0a7a8cbecf14f82.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/bb872e5b506c4fcbb0a7a8cbecf14f82.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/bb872e5b506c4fcbb0a7a8cbecf14f82.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Characters</strong></h2>Characters with unique customizable passives.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/f502a4ffca87e1e6b3752e158beefaeb.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/f502a4ffca87e1e6b3752e158beefaeb.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/f502a4ffca87e1e6b3752e158beefaeb.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Enjoy it!</strong><br>🧛‍♂️",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/e8e845fca660c07d7ce0e3bdaa35538c.gif?t=1765235894\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/e8e845fca660c07d7ce0e3bdaa35538c.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Heroes with unique weapons, abilities, and talents<br></li><li>Over 70 weapons<br></li><li>Weapon fusion system<br></li><li>Over 200 passive abilities for building your build<br></li><li>Racial Abilities<br></li><li>Pets<br></li><li>Runes<br></li><li>Bestiary<br></li><li>Over 20 hours of content<br></li><li>Bosses with unique abilities<br></li><li>Thousands of unlockables<br></li><li>Long character progression<br></li><li>Runs perfectly on Steam Deck<br></li><li>Supports Ultrawide<br></li><li>Day and Night Cycle<br></li><li>Endless Mode</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Starting</strong></h2>Hunt during the day, be hunted during the NIGHT! Fight bizarre monsters that will terrify you at night! Strengthen your hero by collecting relics, familiars from around the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Day & Night Cycle</strong></h2>Look for relics and vendors that only spawn at night.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weather Events</strong></h2>Be prepared!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a8d73bdba79e6492c50e0664.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a8d73bdba79e6492c50e0664.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a8d73bdba79e6492c50e0664.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/bb872e5b506c4fcbb0a7a8cbecf14f82.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/bb872e5b506c4fcbb0a7a8cbecf14f82.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/bb872e5b506c4fcbb0a7a8cbecf14f82.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Characters</strong></h2>Characters with unique customizable passives.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/f502a4ffca87e1e6b3752e158beefaeb.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/f502a4ffca87e1e6b3752e158beefaeb.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/f502a4ffca87e1e6b3752e158beefaeb.mp4?t=17652